Dialogue: 0,00:00:59.520,00:00:59.580,辉英,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:59.580,00:00:59.600,辉英,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:59.600,00:00:59.620,辉英,,0,0,0,,Okay.
