Dialogue: 0,00:05:34.140,00:05:40.140,辉英,,0,0,0,,characteristic go within that very very small range? So what you're going to see
Dialogue: 0,00:05:40.140,00:05:45.560,辉英,,0,0,0,,in a physical solution is there is going to be a fan out there. There is
