Dialogue: 0,00:06:08.080,00:06:16.900,辉英,,0,0,0,,that after a while. Does it make sense? So if you, if you cut the solution over here,
Dialogue: 0,00:06:16.900,00:06:20.880,辉英,,0,0,0,,the solution over here is still minus 1, the solution here is still plus 1,
Dialogue: 0,00:06:20.880,00:06:20.900,辉英,,0,0,0,,okay? So if you cut this both over here, the solution over here is still minus 1,
